blocks.name: ctskm
blocks.content: Extend class definition to include the map whose value is the smallest Tarski class.

blocks.name: df-tskm
blocks.content: A function that maps a set ` x ` to the smallest Tarski class that contains the set. (Contributed by FL, 30-Dec-2010.)

blocks.name: tskmval
blocks.content: Value of our tarski map. (Contributed by FL, 30-Dec-2010.) (Revised by Mario Carneiro, 20-Sep-2014.)
blocks.origin:
thm tskmval(setvar s0, class c0, class c1) {
  |- wi(wcel(c0, c1), wceq(cfv(ctskm, c0), cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))))))
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
} = {
  syl2anc(wcel(c0, c1), wceq(cfv(ctskm, c0), cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))))), wcel(c0, universe), wcel(cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))), universe))
  sylib(wcel(c0, c1), wcel(cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))), universe), wrex(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))))
  sylib(wcel(c0, c1), wrex(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))), wcel(c0, cuni(ctsk)))
  syl6eleqr(c0, cuni(ctsk), universe, wcel(c0, c1))
  elex(c0, c1)
  grothtsk()
  eluni2(s0, c0, ctsk)
  intexrab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))
  fvmptg(hs0, c0, universe, cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))), universe, ctskm, cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(cv(hs0), cv(s0)))))
  inteqd(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(cv(hs0), cv(s0))), crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))), wceq(cv(hs0), c0))
  rabbidv(s0, ctsk, wceq(cv(hs0), c0), wcel(cv(hs0), cv(s0)), wcel(c0, cv(s0)))
  eleq1(cv(hs0), c0, cv(s0))
  df-tskm(hs0, s0)
  diff.ctsk.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(universe)
  diff.hs0.c(cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))))
  diff.wceq.s(s0, cv(hs0), c0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
}
blocks.pretty:
thm tskmval(setvar s0, class c0, class c1) {
  ⊢ (c0 ∈ c1 →(tarskiMap ` c0)= ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 })
  ⊣ d(s0, c0)
} = {
  syl2anc(c0 ∈ c1, (tarskiMap ` c0)= ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 }, c0 ∈ 𝕌, ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 } ∈ 𝕌)
  sylib(c0 ∈ c1, ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 } ∈ 𝕌, ∃(s0 ∈ Tarski, c0 ∈ s0))
  sylib(c0 ∈ c1, ∃(s0 ∈ Tarski, c0 ∈ s0), c0 ∈ ⋃ Tarski)
  syl6eleqr(c0, ⋃ Tarski, universe, c0 ∈ c1)
  elex(c0, c1)
  grothtsk()
  eluni2(s0, c0, ctsk)
  intexrab(s0, ctsk, c0 ∈ s0)
  fvmptg(hs0, c0, universe, ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 }, universe, ctskm, ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | hs0 ∈ s0 })
  inteqd({ s0 ∈ Tarski | hs0 ∈ s0 }, { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 }, hs0 = c0)
  rabbidv(s0, ctsk, hs0 = c0, hs0 ∈ s0, c0 ∈ s0)
  eleq1(hs0, c0, s0)
  df-tskm(hs0, s0)
  diff.ctsk.s(s0)
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(universe)
  diff.hs0.c(⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 })
  diff.wceq.s(s0, hs0, c0)
  diff.cv.s(s0, hs0)
  diffss.ex(s0, hs0)
  diff.hs0.s(s0)
}

blocks.name: tskmid
blocks.content: The set ` A ` is an element of the smallest Tarski class that contains ` A ` . CLASSES1 th. 5. (Contributed by FL, 30-Dec-2010.) (Proof shortened by Mario Carneiro, 21-Sep-2014.)

blocks.name: tskmcl
blocks.content: A Tarski class that contains ` A ` is a Tarski class. (Contributed by FL, 17-Apr-2011.) (Proof shortened by Mario Carneiro, 21-Sep-2014.)
blocks.origin:
thm tskmcl(class c0) {
  |- wcel(cfv(ctskm, c0), ctsk)
} = {
  pm2.61i(wcel(cfv(ctskm, c0), ctsk), wcel(c0, universe))
  eqeltrd(cfv(ctskm, c0), ctsk, cint(crab(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0)))), wcel(c0, universe))
  tskmval(hs0, c0, universe)
  sylancr(wcel(c0, universe), wcel(cint(crab(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0)))), ctsk), wss(crab(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0))), ctsk), wne(crab(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0))), emptycls))
  ssrab2(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0)))
  sylibr(wcel(c0, universe), wne(crab(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0))), emptycls), wrex(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0))))
  sylib(wcel(c0, universe), wrex(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0))), wcel(c0, cuni(ctsk)))
  syl6eleqr(c0, cuni(ctsk), universe, wcel(c0, universe))
  id(wcel(c0, universe))
  grothtsk()
  eluni2(hs0, c0, ctsk)
  rabn0(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0)))
  inttsk(crab(hs0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(hs0))))
  syl6eqel(cfv(ctskm, c0), ctsk, emptycls, wn(wcel(c0, universe)))
  fvprc(c0, ctskm)
  0tsk()
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(ctsk)
}
blocks.pretty:
thm tskmcl(class c0) {
  ⊢ (tarskiMap ` c0)∈ Tarski
} = {
  pm2.61i((tarskiMap ` c0)∈ Tarski, c0 ∈ 𝕌)
  eqeltrd((tarskiMap ` c0), ctsk, ⋂ { hs0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ hs0 }, c0 ∈ 𝕌)
  tskmval(hs0, c0, universe)
  sylancr(c0 ∈ 𝕌, ⋂ { hs0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ hs0 } ∈ Tarski, { hs0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ hs0 } ⊆ Tarski, { hs0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ hs0 } ≠ ∅)
  ssrab2(hs0, ctsk, c0 ∈ hs0)
  sylibr(c0 ∈ 𝕌, { hs0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ hs0 } ≠ ∅, ∃(hs0 ∈ Tarski, c0 ∈ hs0))
  sylib(c0 ∈ 𝕌, ∃(hs0 ∈ Tarski, c0 ∈ hs0), c0 ∈ ⋃ Tarski)
  syl6eleqr(c0, ⋃ Tarski, universe, c0 ∈ 𝕌)
  id(c0 ∈ 𝕌)
  grothtsk()
  eluni2(hs0, c0, ctsk)
  rabn0(hs0, ctsk, c0 ∈ hs0)
  inttsk({ hs0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ hs0 })
  syl6eqel((tarskiMap ` c0), ctsk, emptycls, ¬ c0 ∈ 𝕌)
  fvprc(c0, ctskm)
  0tsk()
  diff.hs0.c(c0)
  diff.hs0.c(ctsk)
}

blocks.name: sstskm
blocks.content: Being a part of ` ( tarskiMap `` A ) ` . (Contributed by FL, 17-Apr-2011.) (Proof shortened by Mario Carneiro, 20-Sep-2014.)
blocks.origin:
thm sstskm(setvar s0, class c0, class c1, class c2) {
  |- wi(wcel(c0, c1), wb(wss(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wss(c2, cv(s0))))))
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s0, c2)
} = {
  syl6bb(wcel(c0, c1), wss(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wss(c2, cv(s0)))), wss(c2, cint(cab(s0, wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0)))))))
  sseq2d(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0), cint(cab(s0, wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0))))), wcel(c0, c1))
  syl6eq(cfv(ctskm, c0), cint(cab(s0, wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0))))), cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))), wcel(c0, c1))
  tskmval(s0, c0, c1)
  inteqi(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))), cab(s0, wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0)))))
  df-rab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))
  3bitr4i(wss(c2, cint(cab(s0, wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0)))))), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wss(c2, cv(s0)))), wal(s0, wi(wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0))), wss(c2, cv(s0)))), wal(s0, wi(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wss(c2, cv(s0))))))
  albii(s0, wi(wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0))), wss(c2, cv(s0))), wi(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wss(c2, cv(s0)))))
  impexp(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wss(c2, cv(s0)))
  ssintab(s0, c2, wa(wcel(cv(s0), ctsk), wcel(c0, cv(s0))))
  df-ral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wss(c2, cv(s0))))
}
blocks.pretty:
thm sstskm(setvar s0, class c0, class c1, class c2) {
  ⊢ (c0 ∈ c1 →(c2 ⊆(tarskiMap ` c0)↔ ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ⊆ s0))))
  ⊣ d(s0, c0)
  ⊣ d(s0, c2)
} = {
  syl6bb(c0 ∈ c1, c2 ⊆(tarskiMap ` c0), ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ⊆ s0)), c2 ⊆ ⋂ { s0 |(s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0)})
  sseq2d(c2, (tarskiMap ` c0), ⋂ { s0 |(s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0)}, c0 ∈ c1)
  syl6eq((tarskiMap ` c0), ⋂ { s0 |(s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0)}, ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 }, c0 ∈ c1)
  tskmval(s0, c0, c1)
  inteqi({ s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 }, { s0 |(s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0)})
  df-rab(s0, ctsk, c0 ∈ s0)
  3bitr4i(c2 ⊆ ⋂ { s0 |(s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0)}, ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ⊆ s0)), ∀(s0,((s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0)→ c2 ⊆ s0)), ∀(s0,(s0 ∈ Tarski →(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ⊆ s0))))
  albii(s0, ((s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0)→ c2 ⊆ s0), (s0 ∈ Tarski →(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ⊆ s0)))
  impexp(s0 ∈ Tarski, c0 ∈ s0, c2 ⊆ s0)
  ssintab(s0, c2, (s0 ∈ Tarski ∧ c0 ∈ s0))
  df-ral(s0, ctsk, (c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ⊆ s0))
}

blocks.name: eltskm
blocks.content: Belonging to ` ( tarskiMap `` A ) ` . (Contributed by FL, 17-Apr-2011.) (Proof shortened by Mario Carneiro, 21-Sep-2014.)
blocks.origin:
thm eltskm(setvar s0, class c0, class c1, class c2) {
  |- wi(wcel(c0, c1), wb(wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0))))))
  -| diffsc(s0, c0)
  -| diffsc(s0, c2)
} = {
  bitrd(wcel(c0, c1), wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0)))), wcel(c2, cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))))))
  eleq2d(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0), cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))), wcel(c0, c1))
  tskmval(s0, c0, c1)
  pm5.21ndd(wcel(c0, c1), wcel(c2, cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))))), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0)))), wcel(c2, universe))
  a1i(wcel(c0, c1), wi(wcel(c2, cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))))), wcel(c2, universe)))
  elex(c2, cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))))
  syl6(wcel(c0, c1), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0)))), wcel(c2, universe), wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)))
  syl5com(wcel(c0, c1), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0)))), wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wcel(c0, cfv(ctskm, c0)))
  tskmid(c0, c1)
  ax-mp(wi(wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0)))), wi(wcel(c0, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)))), wcel(cfv(ctskm, c0), ctsk))
  tskmcl(c0)
  rspcv(s0, cfv(ctskm, c0), ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0))), wi(wcel(c0, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0))))
  imbi12d(wceq(cv(s0), cfv(ctskm, c0)), wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0)), wcel(c0, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)))
  eleq2(cv(s0), cfv(ctskm, c0), c0)
  eleq2(cv(s0), cfv(ctskm, c0), c2)
  elex(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0))
  a1i(wcel(c0, c1), wi(wcel(c2, universe), wb(wcel(c2, cint(crab(s0, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0))))), wral(s0, ctsk, wi(wcel(c0, cv(s0)), wcel(c2, cv(s0)))))))
  elintrabg(s0, c2, universe, ctsk, wcel(c0, cv(s0)))
  diff.ctsk.s(s0)
  diff.wi.s(s0, wcel(c0, cfv(ctskm, c0)), wcel(c2, cfv(ctskm, c0)))
  diff.wcel.s(s0, c0, cfv(ctskm, c0))
  diff.wcel.s(s0, c2, cfv(ctskm, c0))
  diff.cfv.s(s0, ctskm, c0)
  diff.ctskm.s(s0)
}
blocks.pretty:
thm eltskm(setvar s0, class c0, class c1, class c2) {
  ⊢ (c0 ∈ c1 →(c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0)↔ ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0))))
  ⊣ d(s0, c0)
  ⊣ d(s0, c2)
} = {
  bitrd(c0 ∈ c1, c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0), ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0)), c2 ∈ ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 })
  eleq2d(c2, (tarskiMap ` c0), ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 }, c0 ∈ c1)
  tskmval(s0, c0, c1)
  pm5.21ndd(c0 ∈ c1, c2 ∈ ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 }, ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0)), c2 ∈ 𝕌)
  a1i(c0 ∈ c1, (c2 ∈ ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 } → c2 ∈ 𝕌))
  elex(c2, ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 })
  syl6(c0 ∈ c1, ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0)), c2 ∈ 𝕌, c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0))
  syl5com(c0 ∈ c1, ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0)), c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0), c0 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0))
  tskmid(c0, c1)
  ax-mp((∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0))→(c0 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0)→ c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0))), (tarskiMap ` c0)∈ Tarski)
  tskmcl(c0)
  rspcv(s0, (tarskiMap ` c0), ctsk, (c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0), (c0 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0)→ c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0)))
  imbi12d(s0 =(tarskiMap ` c0), c0 ∈ s0, c2 ∈ s0, c0 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0), c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0))
  eleq2(s0, (tarskiMap ` c0), c0)
  eleq2(s0, (tarskiMap ` c0), c2)
  elex(c2, (tarskiMap ` c0))
  a1i(c0 ∈ c1, (c2 ∈ 𝕌 →(c2 ∈ ⋂ { s0 ∈ Tarski | c0 ∈ s0 } ↔ ∀(s0 ∈ Tarski,(c0 ∈ s0 → c2 ∈ s0)))))
  elintrabg(s0, c2, universe, ctsk, c0 ∈ s0)
  diff.ctsk.s(s0)
  diff.wi.s(s0, c0 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0), c2 ∈(tarskiMap ` c0))
  diff.wcel.s(s0, c0, (tarskiMap ` c0))
  diff.wcel.s(s0, c2, (tarskiMap ` c0))
  diff.cfv.s(s0, ctskm, c0)
  diff.ctskm.s(s0)
}
